/ref> Their music have been sampled in numerous occasions,<ref name="TNYIR" /> including by [[Drake (musician)|Drake]],<ref>{{Cite magazine |date=13 February 2019 |title=Every Track From Drake's So Far Gone Ranked: Critic's Picks |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/8498283/drake-so-far-gone-tracks-ranked-anniversary |url-status=live |magazine=Billboard |archive-url=https://archive.today/20211011005505/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/hip-hop/8498283/drake-so-far-gone-tracks-ranked-anniversary/ |archive-date=11 October 2021 |access-date=18 May 2021}}</ref> [[Lizzo]],<ref>{{Cite web |date=14 July 2022 |title=Lizzo Details New Song Called Coldplay, Amid a Surprise Chat with Chris Martin |url=https://americansongwriter.com/lizzo-details-new-song-called-coldplay-amid-a-surprise-chat-with-chris-martin/ |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20220716135727/https://americansongwriter.com/lizzo-details-new-song-called-coldplay-amid-a-surprise-chat-with-chris-martin/ |archive-date=16 July 2022 |access-date=16 July 2022 |website=American Songwriter}}</ref> [[Frank Ocean]],<ref>{{Cite news |date=5 January 2012 |title=Sound of 2012: Frank Ocean |work=BBC News |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-16390456 |url-status=live |access-date=18 May 2021 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20160704222647/http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-16390456 |archive-date=4 July 2016}}</ref> and [[Chance the Rapper]],<ref>{{Cite web |date=11 December 2013 |title=Chance The Rapper Samples Adele and Coldplay On Newly-discovered Mixtapes |url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/chance-the-rapper-69-1239327 |url-status=live |archive-url=https://archive.today/20220117020528/https://www.nme.com/news/music/chance-the-rapper-69-1239327 |archive-date=17 January 2022 |access-date=18 May 2021 |website=NME}}</ref> while also being covered by singers like [[Kelly Clarkson]],<ref name="BILLCOVERS">{{Cite magazine |date=10 March 2021 |title=6 Best Coldplay 